<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-3184] Thrift Go leaves file descriptors open</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3184</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Whenever a post request returns anything but 200, the file descriptor for the connection is left in the OPEN_WAIT state until the program exits leaving the client unusable even after calling client.Transport.Close(). &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
